{
  "ref": "tzhaar-mej-kah",
  "categoryRef": "npc",
  "title": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Standard dialogue",
      "sections": [],
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "lines": [
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "You want help [TzHaar name]?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What is this place?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "This is the fight pit, TzHaar-Xil made it for their sport but many JalYt come here to fight too. If you are wanting to fight then enter the cage, you will be summoned when next round is ready to begin."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Are there any rules?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "No rules, you use whatever you want. Last person standing wins and is declared champion, they stay in the pit for next fight."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Do I win anything?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "You ask a lot of questions. Champion gets TokKul as reward, more fights the more TokKul they get."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "Before you ask, TokKul is like your Coins."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "Gold is like you JalYt, soft and easily broken, we use hard rock forged in fire like TzHaar!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Sounds good."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Ok thanks."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Who's the current champion?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "Ah that would be [TzHaar name]!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What did you call me?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "Are you not JalYt-Ket-Xo-[player name]?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What's a 'JalYt-Ket-Xo'?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "That what you are... you tough and strong no?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Well yes I suppose I am..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "Then you JalYt-Ket-Xo!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What are you then?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "Foolish JalYt, I am TzHaar-Mej, one of the mystics of this city."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What other types are there?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "There are the mighty TzHaar-Ket who guard us, the swift TzHaar-Xil who hunt for our food, and the skilled TzHaar-Hur who craft our homes and tools."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Ah ok then."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Thanks for explaining it."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I guess so..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "Well then, no problems."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "No I'm not!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "TzHaar-Mej-Kah",
              "text": "What ever you say, crazy JalYt!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "No I'm fine thanks."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}